OL,6,FA mum who suffered "one of the worst
OL,7,Fcases of abuse seen by police" says
OL,8,Fshe was finally able to leave her
OL,9,Fviolent partner, when he threatened to
OL,10,Fstab her little boy.
OL,12,FHannah Mellor suffered a campaign of
OL,13,Fsexual, physical, emotional, and
OL,14,Fpsychological abuse over a two-year
OL,15,Fperiod which left her in "constant
OL,16,Ffear" and isolated from her friends
OL,17,Fand family.
