OL,6,FHer former partner, Ben Fitton,
OL,7,Fthreatened to poor boiling water over
OL,8,Fher and "disfigure her for life", as
OL,9,Fwell as strangling and raping her.
OL,11,FAlong with the physical violence, the
OL,12,F33-year-old, from Glossop, in High
OL,13,FPeak, was also controlling and
OL,14,Fcoercive, and "consumed by jealousy,
OL,15,Fparanoia, and anger".
OL,17,FHe controlled when she was allowed to
OL,18,Fshower, and stopped her wearing makeup
OL,19,For brushing her teeth.
