OL,6,F"I wasn't allowed to brush my teeth
OL,7,Ffor the whole time of the
OL,8,Frelationship. It's left me with
OL,9,Fseverely decayed teeth," Hannah said.
OL,11,F"He said, why would I need fresh
OL,12,Fbreath? It could give me an
OL,13,Fopportunity to kiss someone else."
OL,15,FHannah's situation became so bad, she
OL,16,Ftried to take her own life one
OL,17,FChristmas Day.
