OL,6,FShe was then taken to hospital and
OL,7,Flater sectioned, but Fitton parked
OL,8,Foutside in the hospital carpark, and
OL,9,Fwaited for her.
OL,11,FThe turning point came when he
OL,12,Fthreatened to stab her little boy when
OL,13,Fshe tried to leave him.
OL,15,F"I said no, you do what you want to
OL,16,Fme... but you do not come for my boy,"
OL,17,Fshe added.
OL,19,FHannah then made the brave decision to
OL,20,Fcontact Greater Manchester Police
OL,21,F(GMP) via their live chat.
