OL,6,F"I said help me, please help."
OL,8,FFitton, of no fixed abode, was found
OL,9,Fguilty in September 2024 of two counts
OL,10,Fof rape, non-fatal strangulation,
OL,11,Fcoercive and controlling behaviour and
OL,12,Fcausing grievous bodily harm.
OL,14,FHe has been jailed for 18 years, with
OL,15,Fan additional three years on extended
OL,16,Flicense due to the "significant risk"
OL,17,Fthe judge deemed he posed. He was also
OL,18,Fissued a restraining order.
