OL,6,FHannah's waived her right to
OL,7,Fanonymity, with the hope of preventing
OL,8,FFitton from subjecting other women to
OL,9,Fthe same treatment in the future.
OL,11,FShe has this advice for anyone who
OL,12,Ffinds themselves in a similar
OL,13,Fsituation: "Keep going, there is so
OL,14,Fmuch help when you reach for it."
OL,16,F"There was a time I didn't want a
OL,17,Ffuture, there was no future, but
OL,18,Fthere's just so much to look forward
OL,19,Fto now, and not much to look back at."
